    "Details": "Produced as a result of interest from the LCAF, the BZK-D2 removes the UAC/10 of the BZK-D1 and replaces it with a Gauss rifle. The BZK-D2 carried a ton less armor.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stable Weapons</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Upper</color>",
